@vnlitvin since it seems you are more C-comfortable than many contributors, two things that might be up your alley:

- #19361 we have two separate implementations of `xstrtod` that are slightly different.  Last time I tried to de-duplicate them i broke everything.  You might have more luck/talent.
- https://github.com/cython/cython/issues/2570 some of these headers file could/should be implemented upstream in cython
